# Stream Master Document
**Outside Inn & E.I. Werner | 2026 Launch**

---

## Executive Summary

Two interconnected streaming brands launching in 2026: Outside Inn, a 24/7 LoFi radio station, and E.I. Werner, the flagship gaming stream hosted by the Inn. The brands share infrastructure, music, and audience while maintaining distinct identities.

| Milestone | Date | Key Deliverables |
|-----------|------|------------------|
| Beta Launch | March 3, 2026 | 24/7 broadcast, test streams, no monetization |
| Full Launch | June 6, 2026 | Patreon, Discord, socials, posters |
| Album Release | June 6, 2026 | 12-track album, vinyl, NFTs |
| Patron IRL Event | June 6, 2027 | Exclusive in-person event for Patrons |

