## Monetization Strategy

> **Note:** No monetization during Beta (March 3 – June 6, 2026). Ads will be turned off wherever possible to produce a premium listening experience. This forfeits approximately $500–$1,300/month per 1,000 viewers.

### Revenue Streams

#### Gaming Stream Revenue
- **Subscriptions:** Monthly pledges for custom badges, emojis, chat priority. Amazon Prime members can subscribe free.
- **Donations:** Viewers pay to share messages with EIW or chat.

#### Music Licensing & Streaming
- **Royalty-Free License:** $36/mo Innsider tier includes royalty-free rights to use Innspired LoFi music in their own content.
- **Streaming Royalties:** Music distributed on Spotify and Apple Music for passive streaming revenue.

#### Physical Products

| Product | Limited Edition | Stock |
|---------|-----------------|-------|
| Posters | 216 signed, window-like frame | Print on demand |
| Vinyl Records | 216 signed | Print on demand |
| Stickers | N/A | Delivered to $12/mo Patrons |
| Coasters | TBD | TBD |

#### Patreon Tiers

| Tier | Price | Rewards |
|------|-------|---------|
| Patron | $12/mo | Discord access, exclusive tracks via listening room, collectible stickers every other month, IRL event access (06/06/2027), Bronze chat badge (NFT), first 1,296 receive numbered badge |
| Innsider | $36/mo | All Patron rewards + Innsider Discord channel, merch discount, Gold chat badge (NFT), first 216 receive numbered badge, royalty-free music license for personal content |

#### NFT Strategy

**Numbered Badges:** Reward earliest Patrons with numbered chat badges consecrated as NFTs on the blockchain. First 1,296 $12/mo Patrons receive Bronze NFT; first 216 $36/mo Patrons receive Gold NFT. NFTs tied to virtual and IRL rewards.

**Collectible Art:** Mint albums as ultra-rare NFTs.

| Tier | Quantity | Total per Album |
|------|----------|-----------------|
| Master | 1 | 1 |
| Gold | 6 | 6 |
| Bronze | 36 | 36 |

**Total: 43 NFTs per album.**

